window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As Mason strengthens his magic over metal and stone, the Master lurks in the shadows.&nbsp;</p> <p>To lure the Master out and stop his nefarious plot, Mason and his harem of mages and princesses have to do several things:&nbsp;</p> <ol> <li>Take over the Order of Mages&nbsp;</li> <li>Build a train and railroad system to connect the kingdoms of Illaria and Cedis&nbsp;</li> <li>Keep from getting burned by giant, murderous creatures made of flame&nbsp;</li> </ol> <p>Sounds like a piece of cake, right?</p>"; 
